Super Ugly is the best thing the whole dispute spawned...
Fuck the Takeover and Ether debate, I love returning to this song just because Jay-Z destroyed Prodigy. You can't even argue about that one.
I dont care what anyone say, Takeover>Ether. Ether has some corny lines. feels like a mixtape track w/o much thought.

Nas was already on the ropes when Ether was created - let's keep that in mind. Nas managed to dent Jay-Z's rep when he was on top. Now some Jay-Z fans like to get into their head that if if weren't for Takeover, Nas would have had no buzz to feed off and his career continued to stagnate. Well damn, regardless of some undeniably fiery lines and quips, if Jay-Z 'helped' Nas by dissing him then that renders Takeover a bit of a failure in hindsight does it not?!
Ether = better diss. Takeover = better actual song.
Either way those "Yea, I sampled your voice, you were using it wrong" lines are pretty great
